{"tid":1019411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱英醫生踴躍　陳肇始促醫委會研海外註冊醫生須否實習","createTime":"2019-02-13T02:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T00:22:56.000Z","uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fe121c4dd29557f944ddd6bc9c5d3b099a4d9068","tid":1019411,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"醫療人手不足問題存在已久，加上近日正值流感高峰期，導致前線醫護人員壓力「爆煲」，各界狠批政府及醫院管理局多年來束手無策。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始接受電台訪問表示，其實很多海外醫生都有意回港執業，政務司司長張建宗、醫管局主席梁智仁及她過去均曾在英國舉辦簡介會，出席的醫生都反應踴躍，故此會要求醫務委員會研究如何提升「有限度註冊海外醫生」機制的誘因，包括討論海外醫生正式在香港執業前是否要先實習......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213085315232-0213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190213%2Fbkn-20190213085315232-0213_00822_001.html&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=451a5a87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213085315232-0213_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ba9710165efcf51406d7196e6b347046423c1299","tid":1019411,"uid":26770,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:39:09.000Z","msg":"政府又講大話<br />\n外國最盡打15碼<br />\n一日睇幾個症打卡閃人"},{"pid":"a98681506e4b7dfbe9ecc131ec1f2b58982b8dfb","tid":1019411,"uid":221490,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"港女仲唔舉西贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a600f642a436ec1ba7bd39798d544cb4aada6","tid":1019411,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"邊度海外呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4993ff5e6bb65a96fa1274c1362b0c19d9ff7f27","tid":1019411,"uid":26770,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"e32a600f642a436ec1ba7bd39798d544cb4aada6","tid":1019411,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"邊度海外呀<img src=\"/assets/fa